WEBVTT

1
00:00:13.933 --> 00:00:15.200
What do you want?

2
00:00:15.200 --> 00:00:17.200
Brother Ming, give me this.

3
00:00:17.200 --> 00:00:18.566
It's important to us.

4
00:00:19.133 --> 00:00:21.966
I beg you to give me this

5
00:00:21.966 --> 00:00:23.100
I want to save my mother

6
00:00:23.100 --> 00:00:25.133
Brother Ming, this can not only save your mother

7
00:00:25.133 --> 00:00:26.566
And save all mankind

8
00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:28.200
Don't lie to me.

9
00:00:28.200 --> 00:00:29.533
He used one himself

10
00:00:29.533 --> 00:00:31.400
How could this one possibly save all mankind?

11
00:00:31.733 --> 00:00:33.066
Before that

12
00:00:33.133 --> 00:00:35.200
You're not the only one who lost a loved one

13
00:00:35.266 --> 00:00:36.966
Without this serum

14
00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:38.900
After 8 years

15
00:00:39.066 --> 00:00:41.100
Your mother is not alone.

16
00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:43.833
The entire human race will cease to exist

17
00:00:44.566 --> 00:00:45.366
Ningge

18
00:00:45.933 --> 00:00:47.266
We're all doctors.

19
00:00:47.266 --> 00:00:49.233
Do you want to see this result?

20
00:00:49.866 --> 00:00:51.400
Please trust us.

